# Gmail API Configuration for Portfolio Contact Form
# 
# Instructions to set up Gmail API:
# 1. Create a Gmail app password:
#    - Go to: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
#    - Select "Mail" and "Windows Computer" (or your device)
#    - Generate a 16-character app password
#    - Copy it below as GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD
#
# 2. Set your email and recipient email:
#    - GMAIL_USER: The Gmail address to send from (your Gmail)
#    - RECIPIENT_EMAIL: The email address where you want to receive messages (usually same as GMAIL_USER)

# Your Gmail address
GMAIL_USER=your-email@gmail.com

# 16-character app password from Google Account
GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD=phiu npid cgtm mkzn

# Your email address (where to receive contact form messages)
RECIPIENT_EMAIL=b23es1033@iitj.ac.in
